{"tid":203420,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(機械jj入）想問香港搵摩打鋪","createTime":"2017-04-16T09:36:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T17:53:17.000Z","uid":7212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"074a203965ad5979af36a6a484d8038109b12a90","tid":203420,"uid":7212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T09:36:46.000Z","msg":"是咁的，最近要搵d摩打野黎做功課<br />\n諗住上網搵返最原本上頭用緊果舊摩打嘅specif ，無論打咩關鍵字都搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就諗住響香港嘅果d供應商度入手搵下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以想求下名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋關於個motor nameplate <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/16/173448_4ce597143fe36f70ae12961cf90ba8d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F16%2F173448_4ce597143fe36f70ae12961cf90ba8d8.jpg&h=7ed44561&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點解frequency 同speed會有兩個數<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我google過d nameplates 都係得一個數<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利伸 新手，有錯請糾正、屌得細力d<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aed5bad9b98636dee9f8596bcf5cd1d6ac990b4","tid":203420,"uid":7212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T11:10:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd8cd1c58707dc25b98bf0e1dc6fb3084be7416b","tid":203420,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T11:34:05.000Z","msg":"係個range<br />\n最低速同最高速<br />\n50-60hz<br />\n<br />\n要買就淘寶買 淘寶依方面質數唔錯 仲會教埋你<br />\n香港都有得買 新填地街 廣東道果d<br />\n不過賣果d係3相 工業用 大件d<br />\n<br />\n你d細野 係好撚難搵"},{"pid":"bd5e2f578d3ee70003055b5be3dfb4f3dff823e2","tid":203420,"uid":7212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T17:09:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係個range<br />\n最低速同最高速<br />\n50-60hz<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">要買就淘寶買</span> 淘寶依方面質數唔錯 仲會教埋你<br />\n香港都有得買 新填地街 廣東道果d<br />\n不過賣果d係3相 工業用 大件d<br />\n<br />\n你d細野 係好撚難搵</blockquote><br />\n講聲唔該哂先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想問有冇得問佢地拎specif / 圖紙果d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46751399128d0d81872c455c964d3e20e6711249","tid":203420,"uid":74096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T17:14:28.000Z","msg":"1200/1450 好似係講平時行1200，最高可以1450<br />\n<br />\n淘寶容易找到同款，通常有埋datasheet 圖紙 dimensions俾你"},{"pid":"f5deae80876327caee29f7d5edab99f70f7eb037","tid":203420,"uid":7212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T02:23:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1200/1450 好似係講平時行1200，最高可以1450<br />\n<br />\n淘寶容易找到同款，通常有埋datasheet 圖紙 dimensions俾你</blockquote><br />\n岩岩睇過，多數都係拆機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 唔該你先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b0c7a55518732f22cbc2f3ab2dc17ac2258661b","tid":203420,"uid":39431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T02:30:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">1200/1450 好似係講平時行1200，最高可以1450</span><br />\n<br />\n淘寶容易找到同款，通常有埋datasheet 圖紙 dimensions俾你</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb24a320abb15311f4dabed95bf2fe4788e6f7c6","tid":203420,"uid":49727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T04:34:27.000Z","msg":"AC摩打個轉速係用frequency控制<br />\n<br />\n50Hz係1200rpm<br />\n60Hz係1450rpm<br />\n<br />\nbtw 淘寶啦<br />\n不過摩打都唔輕<br />\n注意運費"},{"pid":"79cd5f3be7fcbca5892cb7bd7bbb430129617315","tid":203420,"uid":49727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T04:36:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>AC摩打個轉速係用frequency控制<br />\n<br />\n50Hz係1200rpm<br />\n60Hz係1450rpm<br />\n<br />\nbtw 淘寶啦<br />\n不過摩打都唔輕<br />\n注意運費</blockquote><br />\n因爲日本關東係50Hz<br />\n關西係60Hz<br />\n所以list曬兩個出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66bf42f1e2534529540e72531de2a57063b609f2","tid":203420,"uid":7212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T07:21:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>AC摩打個轉速係用frequency控制<br />\n<br />\n50Hz係1200rpm<br />\n60Hz係1450rpm<br />\n<br />\nbtw 淘寶啦<br />\n不過摩打都唔輕<br />\n注意運費</blockquote><br />\n因爲日本關東係50Hz<br />\n關西係60Hz<br />\n所以list曬兩個出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔該你先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我呀頭叫我留意個火數（power)咁黎揀<br />\n即係要計數啦<br />\n個requirement 係要weight lifting a loading 30kg vertically in 30rpm <br />\n公式就我預有power = torque * speed 、w = mgh/t 、w = Fs = Torque * degree 、Gear ratio 等等<br />\n<br />\n但應該點排個順序去求先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我google 過有鬼仔問過類似野，有人用w=mgv 就解左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但總係覺得冇咁簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c904837afe466f2193eed3713e50afd2c1fe602","tid":203420,"uid":49727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T08:54:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>AC摩打個轉速係用frequency控制<br />\n<br />\n50Hz係1200rpm<br />\n60Hz係1450rpm<br />\n<br />\nbtw 淘寶啦<br />\n不過摩打都唔輕<br />\n注意運費</blockquote><br />\n因爲日本關東係50Hz<br />\n關西係60Hz<br />\n所以list曬兩個出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔該你先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我呀頭叫我留意個火數（power)咁黎揀<br />\n即係要計數啦<br />\n個requirement 係要weight lifting a loading 30kg vertically in 30rpm <br />\n公式就我預有power = torque * speed 、w = mgh/t 、w = Fs = Torque * degree 、Gear ratio 等等<br />\n<br />\n但應該點排個順序去求先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我google 過有鬼仔問過類似野，有人用w=mgv 就解左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但總係覺得冇咁簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小弟讀電<br />\n機械唔太識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果用對重裝置得唔得<br />\n好似lift咁樣<br />\n個moment細好多"},{"pid":"c441c3dc2515e05a1822a878657ff93dd14dbfe5","tid":203420,"uid":7212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T09:09:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>AC摩打個轉速係用frequency控制<br />\n<br />\n50Hz係1200rpm<br />\n60Hz係1450rpm<br />\n<br />\nbtw 淘寶啦<br />\n不過摩打都唔輕<br />\n注意運費</blockquote><br />\n因爲日本關東係50Hz<br />\n關西係60Hz<br />\n所以list曬兩個出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔該你先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我呀頭叫我留意個火數（power)咁黎揀<br />\n即係要計數啦<br />\n個requirement 係要weight lifting a loading 30kg vertically in 30rpm <br />\n公式就我預有power = torque * speed 、w = mgh/t 、w = Fs = Torque * degree 、Gear ratio 等等<br />\n<br />\n但應該點排個順序去求先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我google 過有鬼仔問過類似野，有人用w=mgv 就解左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但總係覺得冇咁簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小弟讀電<br />\n機械唔太識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果用對重裝置得唔得<br />\n好似lift咁樣<br />\n個moment細好多</blockquote><br />\nPulley system <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未必得，因為佢淨係肯比我搞摩打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nElectric <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話個電流都可能會影響到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但小弟電重廢過機械<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76f8ef7547ad693361b2e1e88221ac9621d95f1d","tid":203420,"uid":89220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T09:12:45.000Z","msg":"搵摩打野做功課竟然唔識AC frequency?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"869ad1910776476799e499cb058194410c2e027e","tid":203420,"uid":7212,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T09:16:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵摩打野做功課竟然唔識AC frequency?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSorry ，科電踩線pass <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且上堂冇乜點講過nameplate 呢d live example<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89569ece4158c42e619a3f90b7f3bc482fb1e1b4","tid":203420,"uid":7212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:35:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b1f2177b4a4af5585a56f6735d4866f9e399a8d","tid":203420,"uid":7212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T17:42:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad5a072db4c10b77b8dade2ae51e70fcd4062941","tid":203420,"uid":63017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T17:53:17.000Z","msg":"你要計返個gear box個rates先<br />\n用個力黎配合30rpm"}]}